Andy Comeau https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andy_Comeau 0 Andy Comeau (born October 19, 1970) is an American actor. Comeau's resemblance to Tom Hanks helped him gain the role of Forrest Gump in the 1996 music video for the "Weird Al" Yankovic song "Gump". Comeau is best known for playing Theodore "Teddy" Huffstodt on the Showtime series Huff (2004-2006). He was also featured in the fourth season of the series House as Dr. Travis Brennan in 2007.
